<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Mot de passe oublié</title>
    <% if (message.length > 0){  %>
        <div class="alert">
            <%= message %>
        </div>
        <% } %>
</head>
<style>
    * {
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    .all {
        position: center;
    }
    
    body {
        background-color: #CCE6F4;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }
    
    .container {
        background-image: url(../img/background.png);
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: top center;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        width: 75%;
        padding: 100px;
        margin: 50px;
    }
    
    .container::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 0;
        height: 100%;
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #4BA3C3;
        opacity: 80%;
        z-index: -1;
    }
    
    nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 10px 30%;
        position: relative;
        width: 80vw;
        margin-top: -50px;
    }
    
    li,
    a,
    button {
        font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 400;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    nav img {
        width: 45px;
        height: 30px;
        margin-left: -200px;
    }
    
    .nav-links {
        list-style: none;
    }
    
    .nav-links li {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0px 20px;
    }
    
    .nav-links li a {
        transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;
        color: white;
    }
    
    .nav-links li a:hover {
        color: #fa7f74;
    }
    
    button {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        width: 100%;
        font-size: 18px;
        height: 45px;
        border: 1px solid;
        background: #fa7f74;
        color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
        width: 180px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        outline: none;
        padding: 10px;
    }
    
    button img {
        width: 15px;
        margin: 10px;
    }
    
    .center {
        background-color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 50px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }
    
    .center h1 {
        margin-bottom: 45px;
        margin-top: 15px;
    }
    
    .center p {
        margin-bottom: 45px;
        padding: 10px;
        font-size: 18px;
    }
    
    .num {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    input {
        width: 45px;
        height: 45px;
        padding: 30px;
        margin: 10px;
        border-top: #175676;
        border-left: #175676;
        border-right: #175676;
        background: none;
        outline: none;
    }
    
    .selected-lang {
        cursor: pointer;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        width: 50px;
    }
    
    .selected-lang:before {
        content: '';
        display: block;
        width: 12px;
        height: 12px;
    }
    
    .lang-menu {
        position: relative;
    }
    
    .lang-menu ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: white;
        border: 1px bold #F8F8F8;
        box-shadow: 0px 1px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        display: none;
        position: absolute;
        top: 20px;
        left: 0px;
    }
    
    .lang-menu ul li {
        list-style: none;
        color: #175676;
    }
    
    .lang-menu ul li a {
        width: 50px;
        display: block;
        padding: 3px 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #175676;
    }
    
    .lang-menu:hover ul {
        display: block;
    }
</style>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <img src="../img/whitelogo.png" class="logo">
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/connecter">Se connecter</a></li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#">
                        <div class="lang-menu">
                            <div class="selected-lang">
                                Francais
                            </div>
                            <ul>
                                <li> <a href="#" class="ar">Arabe</a></li>
                                <li> <a href="#" class="eng">Englais</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <div class="center">
            <h1>Mot de passe oublié ?</h1>
            <p>Entrez votre email afin de recevoir un code de connexion: </p>
            <form method="POST" action="/reinitialiser" id="contact-form">
                <input type="email" name="email" required>
        </div>

        <button>Envoyer<img src="../img/fleche.png" alt="arrow"></button>
        </form>
    </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>